	<h2 class="title"><a href="https://alquranmulia.wordpress.com/2017/11/17/tafsir-ibnu-katsir-surah-an-nisaa-ayat-160-162/" rel="bookmark" title="Tafsir Ibnu Katsir Surah An-Nisaa’ ayat&nbsp;160-162">Tafsir Ibnu Katsir Surah An-Nisaa’ ayat&nbsp;160-162</a></h2>
	<a class="date" href="https://alquranmulia.wordpress.com/2017/11/17/tafsir-ibnu-katsir-surah-an-nisaa-ayat-160-162/">
		<span class="day">17</span>
